articles.title: Bohemians' brilliant European run comes to an end after PAOK prevail in Greece - The42
articles.description: First-half goals from Stefan Schwab and Diego Biseswar ultimately downed the Gypsies.
articles.content:
PAOK 2
Bohemian FC 0
(PAOK win 3-2 on aggregate)
BOHEMIANS BOWED OUT of Europe in Greece tonight, as PAOK showed their quality to run out 2-0 winners in their Europa Conference League qualifier se… [+5059 chars]
